response.text:
Based on the search results, the clinical trial NCT02294461 (also known as Asian PREVAIL) primarily investigated the efficacy of Enzalutamide (brand name XTANDI) compared to a placebo in patients with metastatic castration-resistant prostate cancer (mCRPC).

The active ingredient in the XTANDI regimen is Enzalutamide.

Therefore, the ingredient starting with the letter "E" that is part of the more effective regimen is Enzalutamide.

INGREDIENT: ENZALUTAMIDE
